### Prerequisites
### Ansible windows ci config

# Linux System Prep
* Install Babun

* Install python-setuptools
     $ pact install python-setuptools

* Install pip
     $ easy_install pip
     optionally use
     $ easy_install --index-url http://pypi.wg-t.com:8000/wg/dev/ pip

* Install virtualenv
     $ pip install virtualenv virtualenvwrapper

* Install libyaml dev package
     $ pact install libyaml-devel

* Install requrements
     $ pip install -r requirements.txt

* Get Nuget package
     $ nuget install -OutputDirectory aa RegPayment.Deploy

* Execute deploy script
     $ python deploy.py xq ~/code/urp-inventories/wg/qa 0.0.62

* encrypt file
     $  ansible-vault encrypt wg/qa-vars.yaml

* edit encrypt file
     $  ansible-vault edit wg/qa-vars.yaml


#Windows System Prep
* Get-Host

* set-executionpolicy remotesigned (Unrestricted)

* execute script "https://github.com/cchurch/ansible/blob/devel/examples/scripts/upgrade_to_ps3.ps1"

# restart firewall service
* execute script "https://github.com/ansible/ansible/blob/devel/examples/scripts/ConfigureRemotingForAnsible.ps1"


# Test
    $ ansible iis-servers -i ../../urp-inventories/qa/qa -m win_ping  -u xq -k
